  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>쇼핑백도 이제는</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-af1046d5-ad73-45f2-895e-d4e63f38a415\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-500a6f30-1ddb-47c7-b85b-4f769e22e0a7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a724744c-187c-4ec6-bd48-9ae6e79ace56\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-30233220-27f7-46b5-aaf5-71026b00f1c7\" style=\"\">쇼핑백 제작 가이드</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7b77a394-2028-4a15-acf4-42136fbc112f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7b148737-2155-48c9-ad9f-86ac057572c7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c69dc9ce-f089-42ce-a3e6-743ab04ea89f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객 여러분이 쇼핑백을 만든다면 어떤 이유로 무슨 목적으로 제작하실까요? </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bdc0cdd3-e11d-4104-8535-640d10fa5afd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-80631f7a-ee76-44d8-b85c-ce381aefc833\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 다양한 이유와 제작 의도가 있겠지만 단순하게 제품을 구매하는 들것(?)으로만 생산하지는 않을 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-43610e61-6243-4b41-8478-dd3aea91cc47\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8ba26976-6e0b-4d22-af3b-d2bd7df7d406\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0347ce43-1a58-41a8-87f3-6c2c867eb1c9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aab56e15-b08c-41eb-a2f0-6b340345b2a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">쇼핑백이야말로 단순한 포장재의 개념을 넘어 브랜드의 아이덴티티(BI) 또는 회사의 컴퍼니 아이덴티티(CI)를 강화하는 하나의 요소입니다. 이는 패키지와 더불어 그 제품의 브랜드를 소비자에게 각인시키는 하나의 수단으로 자리매김했다는 증거일겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4b258258-bd15-462d-a982-994e29e0b191\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bb670608-8321-4a72-b188-6cf07e5466d0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9fec044e-3fc2-43f9-b2fa-2b3f27010fba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-924e4bdb-d2d7-4fbe-9811-5565f24e20b5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 쇼핑백에서의 요소는 그 브랜드를 알리는 중요한 포인트 중에 하나로 종이 선택, 손잡이, 그리고 디자인까지 모두 브랜드의 관점에서 봐야 할 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-53dcd859-6ed0-420b-9162-b4cab1a6f03a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-615b8702-e70e-4e49-83b0-57e2fd007aa3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-af6c68f1-5655-496e-903f-87419de4526f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a759845b-127d-494b-b6ba-38735132f619\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇기 때문에 쇼핑백 손잡이 끈에도 브랜드 컬러를 도입하거나 또는 지질도 브랜드와 유사한 컬러 또는 친환경 등등의 소재를 선택하는 이유가 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1bd2f092-a010-4bfe-b468-d0c161f69d35\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b8c4ac56-a1f4-4c87-972b-44a3c64ba42b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-33e91270-a6d8-47d2-9e4c-bc6e422ccaad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1c305518-f09f-40e2-a687-e2af1880ebc9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f1c04923-fde1-4be9-a903-00bdea8eea2a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-17ed2956-e47e-4554-bc51-dce404b62424\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-57b96b16-d897-4d4f-adb9-564ea1f08a77\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b481fd86-22ca-462c-b95e-93af3fbc09b2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dc402e06-2d55-4786-b846-30e5953e7e0b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a259b296-d1d9-42e9-b6b0-905ce7b9bfef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">쇼핑백에서 가장 중요한 디자인 요소는 아무래도 컬러일 것입니다. 쇼핑백의 브랜드 컬러는 그 대표적인 제품의 컬러와도 매치되는 가장 중요한 요소입니다. 컬러의 매칭 속에 CI/BI의 배치가 관건입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-89ad5428-bc2c-4346-b687-7baa330d2af1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-98d98f6b-d2f3-4660-9d66-af4eb0ca3872\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1da2cb42-c60d-4d44-a339-52bdfcb02acb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5179d27f-109a-4d96-ad89-d831f5d1bf81\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>컬러</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f6c448ab-4542-430f-9b5d-dfb8c11c5c73\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 제품 또는 회사의 브랜드 컬러를 활용하여 디자인하는 것이 중요합니다. 브랜드에 맞는 컬러가 대표 쇼핑백의 메인 컬러가 될 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2960f82a-3944-4984-9abf-04a2e8646fcc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:491px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-99f4b009-bf67-4be5-a318-ec9cf243f0bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ff4d1fbf-50ae-4103-98a9-919b3a31024a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f64f6d74-4981-4822-8f43-88683bc2ee28\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">자사가 제작 대행한 하늘채의 브랜드 컬러입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-446c6046-c139-4794-994d-8427398c1fad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7bec8114-c730-4114-ab4a-cce02b800d6c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5e60df9a-2581-482f-87db-32df14efee9f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bd0c4eb6-2bf5-49e1-9520-d7ce69ec6d67\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>로고/슬로건</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a27e6b62-f880-4a3f-b42e-56f212dd1427\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 통상의 경우 로고 및 슬로건 등은 심플하게 중앙 배치를 합니다. 다만 특별한 디자인 컨셉을 가져갈 경우 그 배치는 변경될 수 있습니다. 또한 이 부분에 박인쇄나 형압등의 후공정을 가미할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-6004bb55-1585-49e4-a6f4-4502a3c0b162\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d7ef0ae1-53c5-4790-8941-39370cc8761f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-beff986e-0d6d-4af6-a38e-db28f07acd3b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3ca3708b-9716-4566-83de-14609c140da6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>이미지, 그래픽 요소</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fcba3558-e425-4364-a370-086acdfa70d8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 로고만으로 부족하다고 싶다면 그 차별화를 위해 이미지 요소를 추가할 수 있습니다. 그 요소는 너무나 다양합니다. 이미지가 될 수도 있고 패턴이나 문양을 넣을 수도 있으며 또는 이벤트성의 강조점을 추가할 수도 있습니다. 예를 들어 추석이면 추석에 맞는 문양을 깔고 조합하여 디자인하는 등의 부분을 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4e6d1c4d-2425-4e45-8bd6-617a441b9239\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:312px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-71c579e2-5b72-4c79-8d9f-6432d9eacceb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-54c198ba-9499-4f4f-9dce-c61fab4658a3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-842ad990-5c47-402f-b523-a63f0334dc55\" style=\"color:#555555;\">코오롱은 하늘 이미지를 은은하게 깔고 그 요소를 부각시켰습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-92eeadcd-61b8-415c-bc9c-6a8aa7f27a40\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4ba3ac2d-3b9d-4afb-9689-737d72a5a857\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-476c0640-23d8-4630-887d-e4aa60932cfd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-20e35268-9119-413c-8289-06bf7008b908\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de35d514-ca7c-4593-984a-a262f1d18fa0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 코팅/박인쇄/형압/에폭시등으로 그 고급스러움을 올려 퀄리티를 높일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-9acc4069-ef3a-4bd2-9d70-304745f09e64\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e77838be-27fd-41f1-a9dc-62ad97d2c3fb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-cca115e5-84c7-41d9-9c00-49333bd32585\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9edebcaa-1b67-4755-ad8f-01d1715994b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-25132786-bbd5-4b37-b8fc-89fc8e8e6b8a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c8187b0d-d569-4231-a525-d95a79ff2f22\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-26dd3ef4-ba3c-488a-a88c-fe2178d2e858\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05f3a3eb-2071-416d-a499-5e4420ab16d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-51b40720-9c5c-4a81-9820-eb4bf3949c84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-18ab779e-7023-446f-9e84-b58d4bb4b879\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 일반적인 종이는 아무래도 아트지/스노우지입니다. 인쇄 발색이 좋고 가장 탄성도 좋아서 쇼핑백으로 가장 많이 사용됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0a79fa8f-703d-4197-a8a8-09bf2773b416\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8c0c66f0-d4c0-421d-aa76-e8c59c762cd8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">150g ~ 200g 사이가 가장 일반적인 평량입니다. 정리하면 아트지 유광에 스노우지 무광이 가장 선호하는 선택입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-53546a89-8897-46d5-bc67-ca32e2373226\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a0051c63-ec7d-4b19-abdd-801ac839fb8d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-45a27519-b77f-4a8c-b33d-4d2d15e6820a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ce3cf731-dccf-46e6-9d47-2a103e36ca65\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 요즘 크라프트지도 많이 사용되고 있는 추세입니다. 환경친화적이면서 내구성도 좋아서 제품을 담기에 적합하다고 생각합니다. 음식점이나 요식업의 쇼핑백에는 크라프트지가 가장 많이 사용되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0c3bebed-f469-4689-9ce9-20de504a54bf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2f4aced7-c3dd-4fb1-86b8-10b8bcf68ec5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e8c4e76b-1133-427e-866d-c249007686ad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-04e4526c-100a-4e28-9e89-5a755508ef64\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이외에 브랜드의 독창성을 높이기 위한 종이로 색지, 엠보싱지, 메탈릭지, 또는 금/은 보드지 등이 활용되고 있습니다. 하지만 단가가 상대적으로 높아서 고급 브랜드에 한정하여 제작되고 있는 실정입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca9381ba-ec95-4adb-992b-c81f1c92458e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\" style=\"max-width:660px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28270f62-b122-4279-ad99-d9dde78ac176\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-598d5302-6c11-4429-8699-04a8551559f0\" style=\"\">크라프트지 kraft</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-24e7dbd9-968a-434f-b535-62208f4a4d85\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5768835e-898e-489f-b7cf-9adce5032b40\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7d134886-0c61-4ec9-8092-e3c7991e7b7c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-bf23f03e-7c4d-4736-8792-20f1f415c5ae\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d9d34b76-e557-439c-9806-1eec87628fe7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>부자재</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b53b39f2-738d-4976-bc93-a79e24d82002\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-61558ea1-c3ba-4764-9bcf-3a9a02f41498\" style=\"color:#555555;\">------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8cedbdb9-e526-4c88-8b37-d76cfbe712e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8146af21-f0e5-4d0b-93bf-ec2ed1d04785\" style=\"color:#555555;\">쇼핑백에서 부자재는 주로 끈을 말합니다. 끈도 여러 종류가 있고 철핀이나 하도메하고 불리는 부자재도 존재합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-71c0eb77-e87c-456b-ae3d-7a651991558d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1b917bd7-2a0d-42dc-b6a7-ee009b982b05\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-4f59cdcf-1f2e-4263-a889-3eff91ec4d22\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-36009d74-1ab1-4f6a-9060-c303f132e1af\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정확한 용어는 모르지만 쇼핑백 끈 쪽이나 하단에 마분지를 넣어서 보호하는 용으로 부자재가 존재합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0ad73c1e-2e70-4211-a07a-a515c5dbd77c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cc176cf7-3058-4c05-bb53-40d79f268867\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-32052d02-8e12-4935-8215-e31eb8893ca2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4bfdd54e-888a-4b56-9a11-7db5b3e76742\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8686d87a-bf20-4ebb-a926-194bc47cd7f9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dded7ba8-323f-439f-a0f6-a3f3412eb3fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">끈 쪽에 보호를 위해 아일렛(하도메)을 끼우거나 또는 철핀으로 제작합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0f7d1759-8d76-41f8-9e3b-04e9dc24f21a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24410dd1-b147-4259-bb58-6f0bc5b9a5fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f9e9161-1cb7-4dbd-abb0-00a1949752c3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223833630432/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-df1916f8-3b51-4a27-92e2-bef023cc3a4c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-53949ef9-9b24-4586-9994-8b842ecf2bf6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7674791d-b7d3-4e1a-a28b-975862aa7982\" style=\"color:#555555;\">끈은 pp브래이드부터 다양하게 있습니다. 브랜드에 맞는 끈의 선택도 무척 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-205f56cf-6508-43f0-8c63-7f1df11ce934\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa9fa336-47e6-49e7-b24c-e50748c1b225\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-66acd7c2-40ac-4164-aae2-045d3b318c3a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1b11978-9921-4519-a7a6-aebdd7d4671a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c7f068c4-44fb-4c36-a724-b0d24b74af67\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>결론</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-65203d05-d929-4afe-ba34-357e42f851b3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-8c6510d7-9b08-4d52-9c23-b157433ce117\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f236cb76-b2f8-4a11-963e-5a48d2695ffb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이로 만든 쇼핑백은 단순한 포장이나 제품 보호를 위해 제작되지는 않습니다. 쇼핑백을 들고 다니는 소비자가 그 브랜드의 가치를 알고 시각적으로 각인시키는데 주요한 제작 의도가 숨어 있을 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-51da6e28-43e3-4c52-a994-9830f132d24a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3c3aaedd-8eda-464c-ae07-b2d73e1192bc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-421a6c9c-d853-4ce3-90ad-6aeb58611591\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6ac4287-3fec-4d8e-be75-af8848f1f74b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇기 때문에 그 브랜드를 각인시키기 위해 시각적으로 잘 인지시키는 요소들을 조합하는 것이 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-81120b74-ca27-4323-8d25-51c27a62703d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05e9f9e9-8744-46de-9273-f27cbae2a62d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d6d81c6a-c91f-4c45-bb1b-7d06c7106305\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-05e0fadd-7f64-498c-8887-62d7f3a9e288\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대부분의 통화 고객님께서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b3aac7e2-4de4-4e1b-9a60-8225f0dca43d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>\"그냥 중앙에 로고 하나 넣을 건데요?\"라고</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6196adc6-866e-44dd-8bac-fda65909c128\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 말씀을 주십니다. 물론 맞는 요청이지만 쇼핑백을 제대로 만들기 의해서는 다양한 부분을 고려하여 생산할 것을 말씀드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-b6d840ad-d3de-4568-b9ec-e73514667797\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b3238129-72df-45be-a596-0a831fb34f6d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-c2189f48-cded-4cf6-b49e-e2c0eb3c40c3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f3c57c0f-b367-4f2a-930f-f10383e568dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위에서 말씀드린 디자인, 지질, 부자재, 후공정 등을 판단하시어 회사의 브랜드 가치를 높일 수 있는 그런 쇼핑백을 제작하시기를 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a663632a-2122-4ffb-a709-d6cfe532ad44\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ca949f9b-3494-4c3e-bf99-c83bd16c3eeb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-95b52c0c-0eb3-47a8-92a9-1596fcf56bf8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fe9e45c3-9284-4527-b8eb-dde3991af74d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#bdfbfa;\">그런 요청을 잘 수용하여 제작해 드리는 것이 저희 (주)파파스컴퍼니이 가장 잘할 수 있는 일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223833630432#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}